
<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color"><em><a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://tsukinomayu.com/mead-gundam/" target="_blank">Mead Gundam</a></em> is a 321-page book featuring design drawings, concept sketches, and notes &amp; annotations by the late Syd Mead pertaining to his work on&nbsp;<em>Turn A Gundam</em>. Below is a translation of the closing comments by Syd Mead himself. I&#8217;ve also included the additional comments he provided for the 2013 re-print edition of the book.</p>



